          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                " (1)A layer of spectroscopically pure gold metal of",
                "thickness 300 mu-g/cm**2 was evaporated onto a 0.025 cm",
                "thick blank of spectroscopically pure tantalum",
                "which had been previously outgassed in vacuo at red",
                "heat to reduce fluorine contamination. It was",
                "subsequently determined by measuring the width of the",
                "observed photopeaks of gamma-rays from the nonresonant",
                "Li-6(p,gamma0)Be-7 reaction that the alloy layer was",
                "50 keV thick to 600 keV protons.",
                " (2) Thinner target was prepared by direct evaporation",
                "of lithium oxide isotopically enriched to 99% 6Li onto",
                "a 0.025 cm thick fine gold substrate.",
                "The Li content of this target was determined using the",
                "narrow resonance in the Li-6(alpha,gamma)Li-10 reaction",
                "at an alpha-particle bombarding energy of 1175 keV as",
                "in paper of F.Ajzenberg-Selove (see REL-REF)."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "REL-REF": [
